            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinto</ex></expan> Volusio <expan><abbr>Q</abbr><ex>uinti</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilio</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>n</abbr><ex>epoti</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/>Saturnin<supplied reason="lost">o</supplied> <lb n="3"/>auguri salio Pal<supplied reason="lost">atino</supplied> <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>IIIvir</abbr><ex>o</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>uro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>rgento</ex></expan> <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>ere</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>lando</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>eriundo</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="5"/>praefecto <supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>fer</abbr><ex>iarum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Lat</abbr><ex>inarum</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="6"/><supplied reason="lost">ce</supplied>nturioni eq<supplied reason="lost"><expan><abbr>u</abbr><ex>itum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>Rom</abbr><ex>anorum</ex></expan></supplied> <lb n="7"/><supplied reason="lost">tu</supplied>rmae pr<supplied reason="lost">imae</supplied> <lb n="8"/><supplied reason="lost" cert="low">Di</supplied>dymus <supplied reason="lost" cert="low">lib(ertus) fec(it)</supplied>
            </ab></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Datierung: Der Geehrte war 92 n. Chr. ordentlicher Konsul; er wurde etwa um 60 n. Chr. oder bald davor geboren; seine Designation zum Quästor erfolgte wohl im Alter von 24 Jahren und ist in der Inschrift noch nicht aufgeführt. (B): Eck: Z. 2: Saturnino; AE 1972: Z. 4: [vi]r(o); Le Bohec: Z. 4: a(ere); Le Bohec: Z. 7: primae.</p>
            </div>
